OL,3,CGibraltar's monkey's eat mud 'to
OL,4,Csoothe upset stomachs from tourist
OL,5,Cjunk food'
OL,7,FScientists have observed monkeys
OL,8,Fdeliberately eating mud in Gibraltar,
OL,9,Fin what they believe is a reaction to
OL,10,Fconsuming foods like ice cream and
OL,11,Fchocolate bars that upset their
OL,12,Fstomachs.
OL,14,FA population of around 230 Barbary
OL,15,Fmacaques inhabiting the Rock of
OL,16,FGibraltar attract hundreds of
OL,17,Fthousands of visitors annually, who
OL,18,Ffrequently flout rules banning them
OL,19,Ffrom feeding or touching the monkeys.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
