CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776898985
OL,3,CGibraltar's monkey's eat mud 'to
OL,4,Csoothe upset stomachs from tourist
OL,5,Cjunk food'
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe macaques are unable to digest milk
OL,13,Fafter weaning, so they might
OL,14,Fexperience the symptoms of an upset
OL,15,Fstomach after eating ice cream or
OL,16,Fdairy-rich junk foods, said Lemoine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
